      <p class="footer-info">This website was created by a student of Wroclaw University of Technology.&emsp;<a href="#">Contacts</a></p>
      <p class="footer-license">Copyright &copy; 2016 FitIt, Inc.</p>
  </footer> -->

</body>
</html>
